suggestions.original: To further enhance the color contrast in the artwork, consider adding more defined outlines or shadows to the characters and objects. This will help them stand out more against the vibrant background. Additionally, using complementary colors for the background and the characters' clothing can create a more dynamic visual effect. For instance, pairing the red dress with a green background or the blue skirt with an orange background can make the characters pop even more. Lastly, adding some gradient or texture to the background can provide depth and make the scene more visually interesting.
